  renderTableData() {
    return this.state.products.map((product, index) => {
       const { bus_type, source, destination, ddate, departure_time, arrival_time, fare, stops, available_seats,status, booking } = product //destructuring
       return (
          <tr key={Math.floor(Math.random() * 30)}>
             <td>{bus_type}</td>
             <td>{source}</td>
             <td>{destination}</td>
             <td>{ddate}</td>
             <td>{departure_time}</td>
             <td>{arrival_time }</td>
             <td>{fare}</td>
             <td>{stops}</td>
             <td>{available_seats }</td>
             <td>{status}</td>
             <td>{booking}</td>
          </tr>
       )
    })
 }

  render() { //Whenever our class runs, render method will be called automatically, it may have already defined in the constructor behind the scene.
      const { products } = this.state;
    return (
      <div>
        <ReactTable
          data={products}
          filterable
          defaultFilterMethod={(filter, row) =>
            String(row[filter.id]) === filter.value}
          columns={[
            
                {
                  Header: "Bus Type",
                  accessor: "bus_type",
                  id: "bus",
                  filterMethod: (filter, row) => {
                    if (filter.value === "all") {
                      return true;
                    }
                    if (filter.value === "Normal") {
                      return row[filter.id] ==="Normal";
                    }
                    else if (filter.value === "Gold Class") {
                      return row[filter.id] ==="Gold Class";
                    }
                   else if (filter.value === "Luxury") {
                      return row[filter.id] ==="Luxury";
                    }            
                  },
                  Filter: ({ filter, onChange }) =>
                    <select
                      onChange={event => onChange(event.target.value)}
                      style={{ width: "100%" }}
                      value={filter ? filter.value : "all"}
                    >
                      <option value="all">Show All</option>
                      <option value="Normal">Normal</option>
                      <option value="Gold Class">Gold Class</option>
                      <option value="Luxury">Luxury</option>
                    </select>
                },
                {
                  Header: "Source",
                  accessor: "source",
                  id: "sour",
                  filterMethod: (filter, row) => {
                    if (filter.value === "all") {
                      return true;
                    }
                    if (filter.value === "Faisalabad") {
                      return row[filter.id] ==="Faisalabad";
                    }
                    else if (filter.value === "Lahore") {
                      return row[filter.id] ==="Lahore";
                    }
                   else if (filter.value === "Islamabad") {
                      return row[filter.id] ==="Islamabad";
                    } 
                    else if (filter.value === "Multan") {
                      return row[filter.id] ==="Multan";
                    }            
                  },
                  Filter: ({ filter, onChange }) =>
                    <select
                      onChange={event => onChange(event.target.value)}
                      style={{ width: "100%" }}
                      value={filter ? filter.value : "all"}
                    >
                      <option value="all">Show All</option>
                      <option value="Islamabad">Islamabad</option>
                      <option value="Multan">Multan</option>
                      <option value="Lahore">Lahore</option>
                      <option value="Faisalabad">Faisalabad</option>
                    </select>
                
                },
                {
                  Header: "Destination",
                  id: "dest",
                  accessor: "destination", 
                  filterMethod: (filter, row) => {
                    if (filter.value === "all") {
                      return true;
                    }
                    if (filter.value === "Faisalabad") {
                      return row[filter.id] ==="Faisalabad";
                    }
                    else if (filter.value === "Lahore") {
                      return row[filter.id] ==="Lahore";
                    }
                   else if (filter.value === "Islamabad") {
                      return row[filter.id] ==="Islamabad";
                    } 
                    else if (filter.value === "Multan") {
                      return row[filter.id] ==="Multan";
                    }            
                  },
                  Filter: ({ filter, onChange }) =>
                    <select
                      onChange={event => onChange(event.target.value)}
                      style={{ width: "100%" }}
                      value={filter ? filter.value : "all"}
                    >
                      <option value="all">Show All</option>
                      <option value="Islamabad">Islamabad</option>
                      <option value="Multan">Multan</option>
                      <option value="Lahore">Lahore</option>
                      <option value="Faisalabad">Faisalabad</option>
                    </select>
                },
                {
                  Header: "Departure Date",
                  id: "ddate",
                  accessor: d => d.ddate,
                  filterMethod: (filter, rows) =>
                   matchSorter(rows, filter.value, { keys: ["ddate"] }),
                  filterAll: true
                },
                {
                  Header: "Departure Time",
                  id: "departure_time",
                  accessor: d => d.departure_time,
                  filterMethod: (filter, rows) =>
                  matchSorter(rows, filter.value, { keys: ["departure_time"] }),
                  filterAll: true
                },
                {
                  Header: "Arrival Time",
                  id: "arrival_time",
                  accessor: d => d.arrival_time,
                  filterMethod: (filter, rows) =>
                  matchSorter(rows, filter.value, { keys: ["arrival_time"] }),
                  filterAll: true
                },
                {
                  Header: "Fare",
                  id: "fare",
                  accessor: d => d.fare,
                  filterMethod: (filter, rows) =>
                  matchSorter(rows, filter.value, { keys: ["fare"] }),
                  filterAll: true
                },
                {
                  Header: "Available Seats",
                  id: "available_seats",
                  accessor: d => d.available_seats,
                  filterMethod: (filter, rows) =>
                    matchSorter(rows, filter.value, { keys: ["available_seats"] }),
                    filterAll: true
                },
                // {
                //   Header: "Status",
                //   id: "status",
                //   accessor: d => d.status,
                //   filterMethod: (filter, rows) =>
                //   matchSorter(rows, filter.value, { keys: ["status"] }),
                //   filterAll: true
                // },
                {
                  Header: "Status",
                  accessor: "available_seats",
                  id: "over",
                  Cell: ({ value }) => (value > 0 ? "Available" : "Unavailable"),
                  filterMethod: (filter, row) => {
                    if (filter.value === "all") {
                      return true;
                    }
                    if (filter.value === "true") {
                      return (<button>Book</button>);
                    }
                    return  (<button disabled>No Book</button>);
                  },
                  Filter: ({ filter, onChange }) =>
                    <select
                      onChange={event => onChange(event.target.value)}
                      style={{ width: "100%" }}
                      value={filter ? filter.value : "all"}
                    >
                      <option value="all">Show All</option>
                      <option value="true">Available</option>
                      <option value="false">Unavailable</option>
                    </select>
                },
                {
                  Header: "Booking",
                  accessor: "available_seats",
                  id: "seats",
                  Cell: ({ value }) => (value > 0 ? "Available" : "Unavailable"),
                  filterMethod: (filter, row) => {
                    if (filter.value === "all") {
                      return true;
                    }
                    if (filter.value === "true") {
                      return row[filter.id] > 0;
                    }
                    return row[filter.id] <= 0;
                  },
                  Filter: ({ filter, onChange }) =>
                    <select
                      onChange={event => onChange(event.target.value)}
                      style={{ width: "100%" }}
                      value={filter ? filter.value : "all"}
                    >
                      <option value="all">Show All</option>
                      <option value="true">Available</option>
                      <option value="false">Unavailable</option>
                    </select>
                }
              ]
           }
          defaultPageSize={10}
          className="-striped -highlight"
        />
        <br />
       
      </div>
    );
  }
}

export default  Schedule;
